WEBVTT

00:00:05.809 --> 00:00:08.810
How can you have a happy family?

00:00:08.810 --> 00:00:15.300
Notice this sound advice.

00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:19.300
Each one of you must love his wife as he does himself.

00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:24.300
And the wife should have deep respect for her husband.

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:34.609
